node.text:
OMG so FRESH😍 Cut and vacuumed packed Rainbow Box from @greenies.sg. I always have faith in greenies product. Even Mama is impressed with the freshness of the veggies. We can Skip a few trips and queue, also the hassle of cutting/peeling plus Vacuumed pack stay fresh longer! ⠀
⠀
My Box A with 12 freshly sealed packs of veggies is only $30. If u hit $39 gets FOC delivery! Got a box with the LATEST dim sum lion mane gyoza, wontons and HK BBQ buns. Deliver a box to your elderly love ones ask them stay at home!⠀
⠀
Check out the website http://greenies.com.sg or their page  @greenies.sg @glife .
